OL,4,CCovid in Scotland: End-of-life visitors
OL,5,C'need quarantine support'
OL,6, A woman who travelled from Turkey to
OL,7, see her dying father no longer has to
OL,8, quarantine in a hotel after criticising
OL,9, the lack of mental health support.
OL,11,FClaire Herriot, from Glasgow, flew home
OL,12,Fto visit him in hospital after being
OL,13,Fadvised she would be allowed a one-off
OL,14,Fcompassionate visit.
OL,16,FShe said being kept in a hotel was
OL,17,Fadding to the trauma of saying goodbye.
OL,19,FOn Friday the deputy chief medical
OL,20,Fofficer allowed her to leave after
OL,21,Fruling her case was "exceptional".
